<br>
I like the idea that you get faction...as you are the one that ordered your pet to kill the mob.  It was nice however to have the pet go kill green things and not suffer the &quot;penalty&quot; of faction hits...you could get one from a level 1 nuke if you really wanted it.<br>
<br>
Had anyone else noticed this?<br>
<br>
What do you think?  Good or Bad?<br>
